{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC06_NIO_510.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x25,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hmhmhmmm♪<CR>Hmmm, hmhmmhmm♪"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x12,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm, that humming means your synthesis is going well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yup. I was just thinking that today's synthesis is going‐"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Huh!? Nio!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1d9,
            "expr_id": 0x1,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Yup. It's me.<CR>Hi, Sis."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Nio, but what're you doing here now...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1d9,
            "expr_id": 0x1,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, I wonder... I totally don't know the reason why."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1d9,
            "expr_id": 0x1,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "But all of a sudden, I can tell where you are..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1d9,
            "expr_id": 0x1,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Cuz something smells really nice.<CR>See, even now, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "A nice smell...? Could it be the essential oil that I made from the glowing flowers?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Yeah! I figured out where you are because this is where the smell is coming from."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "If the smell was stronger, it'd be easier to find you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I see. I wonder how it works? You can't really smell the oil unless you're in the room..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "That's not true. No matter how far away it is, it can still reach me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I can smell it...or it's almost like I can see a light."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "From the dark place that I'm always at, I can see this smell..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Nio, I know I've asked you before, but you don't know where you are, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. It's dark and warm...and it's almost fluffy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I don't know anything other than that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "It sounds like you're inside a dream..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, even the candy I got from you last time..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "I've tried so many times, but I just can't open the bag."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "And it's like I'll be running,<CR>but I can't move forward at all."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "The more you describe it to me, the more mysterious it seems. Is there anything else out of the ordinary?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1d2,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "*yaaawn* ...Well, I get sleepy really fast whenever I come outside..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1d4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I'm able to see you now, but when I fall asleep and wake up..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "I'm back in the same place."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Nio, so..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1d2,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "No... I'm getting sleepy again.<CR>Good night, Sis..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "She disappeared... But I think I'm finally getting used to that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "So she's not in a place that's painful, or cold or hot..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "That's a bit of a relief..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Yup, I should be optimistic. I just found some things out right now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "First, that I should make the effects of the essential oil I get from the glowing flowers stronger."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "I still don't know what the flowers are, but I might find something out while I continue my research."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "And for that...I need more glowing flowers!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "Wait for me, Nio.<CR>Your sister will do her best!"
        }
    ]
}